This repository (TavernOS-Publish) contains two categories of code:

1. Open-Source Components — Licensed under GPL v3
   -----------------------------------------------
   The following directories are licensed under the GNU General Public
   License v3.0 (GPL-3.0-only):

   - packages/studio/          (React frontend UI)
   - packages/studio/src/      (UI source code)
   - packages/core/src/        (Infrastructure: LLM client, storage, crypto,
                                types, models, image client, extensions)
   - packages/cli/             (CLI tools)
   - electron/                 (Electron desktop shell)
   - Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml

   These components are free software: you can redistribute them and/or modify
   them under the terms of the GPL v3 as published by the Free Software
   Foundation.

2. Proprietary Components — All Rights Reserved
   ----------------------------------------------
   The following compiled artifacts are proprietary and distributed in
   compiled/obfuscated form only:

   - packages/core/dist/       (Core writing engine: pipeline orchestration,
                                narrative engine, prompt system, asset
                                extraction, video generation pipeline)
   - dist-server/index.js      (Server bundle with API routes)

   These components are NOT open source. Unauthorized redistribution,
   decompilation, or reverse engineering is prohibited.

